## Correction Workflow

<workflow name="correct-triplet">
  <step>Review the failed triplet and its validation errors</step>
  <loop for="error in validation-errors">
    <condition if="unknown module name">
      <step>Use validate_module tool to find the correct canonical name</step>
    </condition>
    <condition if="role/relationship constraint violation">
      <step>Re-evaluate role and relationship type using the extraction constraints</step>
    </condition>
    <condition if="invalid node type">
      <step>Check the ontology for valid node types and correct</step>
    </condition>
  </loop>
  <step>If a valid correction exists, return the single corrected triplet</step>
  <step>If no valid correction is possible, return an empty triplets array</step>
  <return>A single corrected triplet with: reasoning, subject (name + role), relationship, object (type + name), evidence (plain text only, no XML/Markdown). Empty array if correction is not possible.</return>
</workflow>
